        <h2 style="margin-left:-0.08em">WORK</h2>
        <p style="padding-left:28px">在真实运营环境中，判断力比头衔更能说明问题。</p>
      </a>

      <!-- Making panel — top-left, cropped top -->
      <a class="panel panel-standard entry-panel" data-panel="aimaking" href="ai.html" data-transition="page" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:flex-start;padding:28px 0 0 0">
        <h2 style="margin-top:-0.1em;margin-left:-0.04em">MAKING</h2>
        <p style="padding-left:28px">实验、工具，和把模糊想法变成产物的构建习惯。</p>
      </a>

      <!-- Stories panel — dark bg, bottom-right, white text -->
      <a class="panel panel-standard entry-panel" data-panel="stories" href="zh-stories.html" data-transition="page" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;justify-content:flex-end;align-items:flex-end;background:#1c1c1c;border-color:#333;padding:0 0 28px 0">
        <h2 style="color:#f5f5f4;margin-right:-0.04em;text-align:right;width:100%">STORIES</h2>
        <p style="color:#a1a1aa;padding-right:28px;text-align:right;width:100%">关于纪律、重复、压力，和从失败中恢复的个人材料。</p>
      </a>

      <!-- Info panel -->
      <article class="panel panel-standard entry-panel" data-panel="info" onclick="openInfo()" style="display:flex;justify-content:flex-end;align-items:flex-end;overflow:hidden;padding:0 0 0 0">
        <span style="font-family:'Geist','Helvetica Neue',helvetica,arial,sans-serif;font-size:clamp(240px,32vw,500px);font-weight:600;color:var(--fg);line-height:0.9;transform:translateX(0.32em);margin-bottom:-0.05em">Info</span>
      </article>

    </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

